Backend:
- TypeScript
- Prisma (ORM)
- nodemon
- stripe
- postman
- nodemailer
- zod
- JWT authentication
- Express.js
- bcrypt (password hashing)
- cors
- dotenv
- tsx / ts-node
- PostgreSQL (via @prisma/adapter-pg)

Authentication:
    Login — verifies credentials, issues access + refresh token 
    Logout — revokes refresh token, clears cookie 
    Refresh — rotates refresh token (marks old as used), issues new access token 
    withAuth middleware — applied to all mutating routes 
    Ownership checks — in place for all routes with a userId param 
    req.user — attached in withAuth, typed via express.d.ts 

Frontend:
- React Native
- Expo
- expo-router
- React Navigation (native-stack, bottom-tabs, material-top-tabs)
- react-native-paper (UI component library)
- react-native-pager-view
- @expo/vector-icons
- TypeScript

